{"tid":735063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個地鐵最深刻廣告","createTime":"2018-07-09T07:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T13:57:03.000Z","uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3b10468dfd455e45c7aab2334ff2381027138569","tid":735063,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:37:46.000Z","msg":"今日港鐵出咗個新廣告<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/396454395150/posts/10160806723065151/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F396454395150%2Fposts%2F10160806723065151%2F&d=o3r6j3M7AqXltrNppPm1YROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=261901aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/396454395150/posts/10160806723065151/</a><br />\n<br />\n第一次用動畫得 其實個感覺唔差<br />\n先撇除佢加價 故障 工程俹簁<br />\n單單以一個廣告做得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我記得佢以前啲廣告都做得幾好 感覺都好清新<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8Xcv-OqSUE4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8Xcv-OqSUE4&d=o3r6j3M7AqXltrNppPm1YROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c1f085cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8Xcv-OqSUE4</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有呢個<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cghBO0ebC7w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcghBO0ebC7w&d=o3r6j3M7AqXltrNppPm1YROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=6f660ed6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cghBO0ebC7w</a><br />\n<br />\n以前啲廣告係同出版商 新碟一齊出<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n4hxXHmMLKI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn4hxXHmMLKI&d=o3r6j3M7AqXltrNppPm1YROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=cf471f31\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n4hxXHmMLKI</a><br />\n<br />\n當年東涌線真係覺得好正 好新鮮<br />\n<br />\n大家又有冇咩港鐵廣告印象深刻？"},{"pid":"3db02fdf34880693c7a47436cb85cb9b8be05e8e","tid":735063,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:40:36.000Z","msg":"九鐵"},{"pid":"d40cb971bb34e588a42d15bdf3b907d622a3a9fc","tid":735063,"uid":44333,